title: Episode 143 w/ Swizz Beatz

description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys drink it up with returning guest Swizz Beatz. The guys are also joined by guest host Angela Yee. They talk Harvard, Swizz's new album, Lil' Wayne, Nas, relationships and a lot more!
